{"tid":1395567,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登AC比想像中容易拎到，好易比人帶到風向","createTime":"2019-08-01T19:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T19:41:55.000Z","uid":274558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f44af2b4790410f765c93113bd97fc3922f1d45b","tid":1395567,"uid":274558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:31:09.000Z","msg":"我係因為今次反送中先特別搵返之前大專時候的電郵，先發覺原來 alumni 都仍然入到個大專電郵, 仲起碼開到兩個AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好撚多差佬，離地中產，藍絲都有大專，副學士或者文憑等學歷，而家連登咁高調，佢哋要開帳戶入黎傳播恐懼同假訊息真係話咁易。<br />\n<br />\n大家跟風之前真係善用起底功能，思慮周全一D，睇下長遠的後果係乜，有關言論的助長最後對邊一方同埋抗爭局勢有利。唔好咁易比人帶到風向，助長某種不利的言論或者抗爭者之間的不信任的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\nBe Smart! 唔好好似D無腦藍絲咁，人地講幾句朋友話乜乜乜，求其貼句對話或者 cap 圖就信到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"d4e6c0d22adbdac69b8adb0a8cf63b84ddd63453","tid":1395567,"uid":279995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0820826c7cff894855661dd69f6c2b4256edf31d","tid":1395567,"uid":274558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"仲有善用不推人回覆，咪撚將D標題黨五毛 post 屌到上熱門，搞到仲多人睇到佢哋的假清息信以為真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f160683ec1290390101027d1e8412e6e8263e0","tid":1395567,"uid":274558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:44:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4e71b5df6bbfd61c2bd67be669f5c6e0f35f767","tid":1395567,"uid":274558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:50:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a82255fb8